txt.en: You can move your character with the W, A, S and D keys.

Welcome to Lord of the Rings Online! To move, use the following (default) keys: 

<rgb=#FFFF00>W</rgb> - to move forward
<rgb=#FFFF00>S</rgb> - to move backwards 
<rgb=#FFFF00>A</rgb> - to turn left 
<rgb=#FFFF00>D</rgb> - to turn right
